            . The prisoner was my <rs id="t18341016-38-deflabel208" type="occupation">apprentice</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341016-38-defend441 t18341016-38-deflabel208"></join>, and his time had nearly expired - this pair of shoes were found concealed by a lodger - I watched, and saw the prisoner take them about half-past eight o'clock in the evening - he then went into the kitchen, and was there a few minutes - I then followed him into the shop, and told him I would not allow him to go, as he had something about him belonging to me - he said he had not - the officer found these shoes concealed in his breeches.</p>
